13
00:02:16.594 --> 00:02:17.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Cariño,

14
00:02:17.720 --> 00:02:20.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
no volverás a trabajar como asesino, ¿no?

15
00:02:23.852 --> 00:02:26.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
