19
00:02:35.280 --> 00:02:37.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¡El divorcio!

20
00:02:41.786 --> 00:02:43.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bien, solo lo verifico.

21
00:02:43.997 --> 00:02:46.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Iré a barrer afuera.

22
00:02:49.252 --> 00:02:51.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¿Cuál es esa "regla de la familia"?

23
00:02:55.300 --> 00:02:58.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
¡Tiene que dejar de matarme en su mente!

24
00:02:58.469 --> 00:03:00.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Mantén la boca cerrada.</i>

25
00:03:01.097 --> 00:03:02.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
